Read csv files into a master table.

Source: R/master.R
csv_master.Rd

Read csv files into a master table.

csv_master(path)

Arguments

path

Path to directory with equations.csv, sitespecies.csv, and sites_info.csv.

Value

A dataframe.

Examples

csv_master(allodb_example("csv_database"))
